{html}<div><p>Tested the following code on iPhone 4 (4.2.1) and iPhone
Simulator (4.2)<br></p>
<pre>
<code>var win = Titanium.UI.createWindow({backgroundColor:'#ccc'});
var table = Ti.UI.createTableView({});
data = [];
for(var i = 0;i&lt;30;i++){
    var row =Ti.UI.createTableViewRow({});
    var textfield = Ti.UI.createTextField({height:40,width:300,value:i,backgroundColor:'#ccc'});
    row.add(textfield);
    data[i]=row;
    Ti.API.info(i);
}
table.data=data;
win.add(table);
win.open();</code>
</pre>
<p>Ti SDK 1.6 (Jan 25 2011 17:39 r1ead074f)<br>
Working as expected</p></div>{html}
